title: Start
body:
Ali: There is a puppy fell into river!
Ali: What should I do?
[[Save it by a branch.|BranchSave]]
[[Jump into the river|JumpRiver]]
[[Walk away|NoSave]]

title: BranchSave
body:
Ali: I can save it by this branch.
Ali: Still a little bit.
The puppy has been rescue.It seen like very grateful toward Ali.

title: JumpRiver
body:
Ali jump into the river.
Ali drown in the river.
Ali: Help! Help!
A man walk beside the river and notice Ali.
The man jump into the river
People: You should not jump into the river.
Ali: Sorry...

title: NoSave
body:
Ali: It is too dangerous for me to rescue the puppy.
Ali: Someone will save it.
The dog flew away.
Ali: I should rescue it...
